Dirty polluted water
Jul 2023 ‚Ä¢ Family
Once entered, you can see rubbish floating around already. The water is visibly very polluted from mass tourism and also the industrial plants nearby. Locals dumped rubbish into the bay, the whole bay is very crowded with all the ‚Äòluxury cruise‚Äô releasing oil/petro/smoke into the area. There is no such thing as exclusivity when you have hundreds of ships around you, in fact, those cruises are just floating hotels. They barely cruise anywhere. I think they should limit the number of cruises and visitors per day and teach locals about waste management.
