1
5.0 of 5 bubbles
one day tour independently.
Nov 2019
I will not write about Halong Bay, as you all have read about it a lot on net or in books. It is indeed wonderful. I will tell you how to do it independently from Hanoi. Most probably, you will be residing in or ear old quarters area in Hanoi. If you wish you can have one day organised tour at about 29-30 dollars or you can do it independently also. From Hanoi take city bus no. 34 to My Dinh Bus station. Your hotel will tell you from where to take this bus. It passes through opera house also. From My dinh station, there are my bus companies going to BAI CHAY.. Take such one bus to Bai Chay which costs about 100.000 VDong and about 4 hours. The bus is air-conditioned. when you reach Bai Chay station, from there take a motor bike taxi to the jetty as walking is long distance about 3-4 kms which can waste precious time for a day tripper. At the jetty look for where local people are standing in queue and enquire if it is for cruise tour. Tour operators will pester you with their tours. Get the govt boat tour of about 3-4 hours, and return the same way to Hanoi. But, if wish to avoid all these transfers etc, simply take a organised tour as per your budget, the lowest one starts around 29-30 dollars for a day tour from old quarters with lunch. That is also reasonable. If you travel independtly you travel with locals which is a bonus. Decide yourself. Have a nice time.
